{
    "name": "Devourer",
    "type": "monster",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Devourers are the undead remnants of fiends and evil spellcasters who became lost beyond the farthest reaches of the multiverse. Returning with warped bodies, alien sentience, and a hunger for life, devourers threaten all souls with a terrifying, tormented annihilation. These withered corpses stand 10 feet tall but weigh a mere 200 pounds."
        }
    ],
